<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title><%= car.name %> 상세 정보</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>자동차 상세 정보</h1>
    <p><strong>ID:</strong> <%= car._id %></p>
    <p><strong>이름:</strong> <%= car.name %></p>
    <p><strong>가격:</strong> <%= car.price %></p>
    <p><strong>제조사:</strong> <%= car.company %></p>
    <p><strong>연식:</strong> <%= car.year %></p>
    <hr>
    <a href="/list">목록으로 돌아가기</a>
    <a href="/update/<%= car._id %>">수정하기</a>
</body>
</html>